library(cowplot)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)

Volcano plot

Version 1

pval=0.05
fc=1.2
# using p_val instead of p_val_adj
res = res %>% mutate(DE=ifelse(avg_log2FC >= log2(fc) & p_val < pval, 'UP',
                               ifelse(avg_log2FC <= -log2(fc) & p_val < pval, 'DN','no_sig')))
res$DE = factor(res$DE, levels = c('UP','DN','no_sig'))

res %>% 
  ggplot(aes(avg_log2FC, -log10(p_val), color=DE)) + 
  geom_point(size=1, alpha=0.9) + 
  scale_color_manual(values = c('red','blue','grey')) +
  theme_classic() +
  # geom_vline(xintercept = 0, color='black') +
  geom_vline(xintercept = c(-log2(fc),log2(fc)), color='grey') +
  geom_hline(yintercept = -log10(0.05),color='grey') +
  theme(legend.title = element_blank()) +
  guides(colour = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size=5))) +
  ggtitle("TREAT/CTL in Selected group") +
  ggeasy::easy_center_title() + ## to center title
  labs(caption = "version1")

Gene-labeled version (Example)

# Gene Selection 
ps = gsea.res$ID[grepl("INTER",gsea.res$ID)][1]
ps.genes = gsea.res[gsea.res$ID == ps,]$core_enrichment
genes_vector <- unlist(strsplit(ps.genes, "/"))

genes_vector = genes_vector[genes_vector %in% res$gene]

# Filter the genes 
labeled_data <- res[res$gene %in% genes_vector,]
labeled_data[labeled_data$DE !="UP",]$gene = ""
pval=0.05
fc=1.2
# using p_val instead of p_val_adj
res = res %>% mutate(DE=ifelse(avg_log2FC >= log2(fc) & p_val < pval, 'UP',
                               ifelse(avg_log2FC <= -log2(fc) & p_val < pval, 'DN','no_sig')))
res$DE = factor(res$DE, levels = c('UP','DN','no_sig'))

res %>% 
  ggplot(aes(avg_log2FC, -log10(p_val), color=DE)) + 
  geom_point(size=1, alpha=0.9) + 
  scale_color_manual(values = c('red','blue','grey')) +
  theme_classic() +
  # geom_vline(xintercept = 0, color='black') +
  geom_vline(xintercept = c(-log2(fc),log2(fc)), color='grey') +
  geom_hline(yintercept = -log10(0.05),color='grey') +
  theme(legend.title = element_blank()) +
  guides(colour = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size=5))) +
  ggtitle("TREAT/CTL in Selected group") +
  ggeasy::easy_center_title() + ## to center title
  ggrepel::geom_text_repel(data = labeled_data,
                                  aes(label = gene),
                                  box.padding = 0.5,  #     
                                  point.padding = 0.3,  #     
                                   segment.padding = 0.2,  #   
                                  size = 4,
                                  color="grey2",
                                  max.overlaps = Inf) +
  labs(caption = "Selected genes")
